I kissed a girl and I liked it.. Well Max kissed a girl, but I'm not really sure how she felt about it. And, I know David got what was coming to him, but I still feel a little guilty about breaking up a marriage. I need to keep busy to take my mind off of it. So let's continue to uncover the truth behind Rachel's disappearance, shall we.
